{"tid":2197654,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"警方展開「亮劍」行動 拘捕6人涉求職騙案的行騙集團成員","createTime":"2020-09-10T19:00:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-15T15:21:40.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f4a178b4a9b5801b7939f2cabddca8f8e2d182ae","tid":2197654,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T19:00:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/C1Xf-TjhhWqC3fjzCHbA_l_StR4=/802x534/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JNZGMJ3WHJCWBENQ76JJRQFQLM.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FC1Xf-TjhhWqC3fjzCHbA_l_StR4%3D%2F802x534%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJNZGMJ3WHJCWBENQ76JJRQFQLM.JPG&h=fabad8fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n警方拘捕6名男子涉嫌以欺騙手段取得財產，他們透過招聘廣告，聲稱可提供高薪工作而騙財，最少20名受害人，涉及款項230萬元。<br />\n<br />\n新界北總區重案組關駿軒總督察稱，由今年1月至8月，新界北警區共有33宗涉及求職的騙案，較去年同期19宗，有七成的升幅。警方接手調查後鎖定一個行騙集團，於過去兩天（8日及9日）採取代號「亮劍行動」拘捕包括主腦在內的6名骨幹成員。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20200910/IVXUUJHPNBCU3GLI6BONUA42S4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200910%2FIVXUUJHPNBCU3GLI6BONUA42S4%2F&d=u5s3JLQ1HZhTjCUFZ9m1FC%2F0jIrp0bHqVoz25JuQVd4%3D&h=01c5ba54\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200910%2FIVXUUJHPNBCU3GLI6BONUA42S4%2F&h=bffc8199\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20200910/IVXUUJHPNBCU3GLI6BONUA42S4/</a>"},{"pid":"3634eb81a93fcb98d2b503ba01a5a9e746fa4a0c","tid":2197654,"uid":273703,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T19:03:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"325421a8b355a57777e34e8e866e454fb0ca022e","tid":2197654,"uid":273703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T19:04:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5ef8c380049166b4117ddeee